You see the usual large timetable, full to the brim of films you may or may not have seen.
As per usual, a small queue has developed at the desk where you purchase tickets.
As per usual, you note the exits to the room. There is a large door that opens onto the street outside. You have absolutely no intention of using that door. There is also the door that leads towards the screening room, shop and toilets. It appears to be guarded by an elite teen worker.
